videos.description: Julius Randle kicks it out to a wide-open Reggie Bullock and he splashes the 3-pointer as the Knicks lead the Thunder 98-85.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bullock nails a triple from downtown) 2021/3/13 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bullock nails a triple from downtown

videos.description: Julius Randle scores 26 points, 12 rebounds and adds 12 assists to become the first Knicks player since Mark Jackson to record multiple triple-doubles in a single season.
